          "type": "theory",
          "data": {
            "title": "New mark: ាំ (Am) — nasal tone",
            "text": "This vowel mark adds a NASAL quality to the vowel.\n\nIt's like the vowel passes through the nose.\n\nCompare:\n- កា = kaa (clear, open)\n- កាំ = kam (nasal quality)\n\nMoon team:\n- គា = kea (clear)\n- គាំ = koam (nasal with O-coloring)\n\nNotice: the nasal mark ាំ combines with the vowel ា, and Moon team still adds the O-coloring.",
            "sublesson_title": "The Am Mark"
          }
        },
